# Finance Management Module — Complete

## What Was Built

### 4 Mongoose Models (`src/models/`)
| Model | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `FeeStructure.ts` | Defines what a student owes per program/semester |
| `FeePayment.ts` | Tracks all payments (partial + full) per student with embedded transactions |
| `Expense.ts` | Logs college operating expenses by category |
| `Salary.ts` | Monthly salary records with net amount stored for history |

### 9 API Endpoints (`src/app/api/admin/finance/`)
| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/fee-structures` | GET, POST | List and create fee structures |
| `/fee-structures/[id]` | PUT, DELETE | Update (soft-delete if payments exist) |
| `/payments` | GET | List all payments (filterable by session/status) |
| `/payments/[studentId]` | GET, POST | Student payment history + add payment |
| `/expenses` | GET, POST | List/create expenses with month/category filter |
| `/expenses/[id]` | PUT, DELETE | Update and delete expenses |
| `/salary` | GET, POST | Monthly salary records |
| `/salary/[id]` | PUT | Mark salary as paid |
| `/dashboard` | GET | All financial summary stats |
| `/api/student/finance/payments` | GET | Student reads their own fees (read-only) |

### 5 UI Pages
- **`/admin/finance`** — Dashboard with stat cards (Revenue, Expenses, Balance, Pending Fees, Pending Salary) and pending payments table
- **`/admin/finance/payments`** — Searchable student list → payment table with Add Payment modal
- **`/admin/finance/expenses`** — Expense list with month/category filter, totals, Add Expense modal
- **`/admin/finance/salary`** — Monthly salary list, Mark Paid button, Add Salary modal with net preview
- **`/student/fees`** — Read-only fee summary with expandable transaction history and overdue indicators

### Navigation
- `Finance` → linked in **admin sidebar** (Wallet icon)
- `My Fees` → linked in **student sidebar** (Wallet icon)

